// CONTROLS
<ul><li>Press T to start recording</li><li>A - S - D - F      buttons work now for (50) keypresses (or less)</li><li>Press Y to stop recording</li><li>Repeat for two more times</li><li>Press R</li><li>Leave</li></ul>
<p>Its the first one. I leave a bit disappointed because the coding phase went very smoothly but things really slowed down after I opened up blender and I hand barely used it before. But the purpose of this jam for me was to force myself into using blender, 3d animations and figuring out how to playback sounds so I needed to sacrifice all the "gameplay" elements from the "game" and had no time to implement dialoque boxes to loosely fit the jam theme in... But in the end I (barely) did that what I wanted to do but the project absolutely isn't something that I hoped it would have become. I am really satisfied with the code tho :). Still a good first experience I guess +1</p>
